Garuda Analytics Dashboard

Garuda Analytics Dashboard is a full-stack data analytics platform that allows users to upload datasets, analyze them, and generate insights through an interactive web dashboard.

The project demonstrates full-stack development, API design, and machine learning integration using modern technologies.

Live Demo

The project is deployed online.

Frontend:
